§ CREATOR-ATTESTATION
  ¬ harm     ≡ swap-protocol degrades-gracefully ∀ trigger
  sovereignty ≡ unilateral-revert preserved ∀ session-state
  rollback   ≡ no-confirm-dialog ; player-or-host can-execute any-time
  ‼ bound-by PRIME_DIRECTIVE ; ¬ overrideable
